OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fcontinuing to spread east this evening
OL,7,Fgiving a generally wet night, although
OL,8,Fthe rain perhaps easing a little
OL,9,Flater. Rather windy on southern coasts
OL,10,Fand breezy inland, though winds easing
OL,11,Flater. Staying very mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA damp start with some drizzly
OL,14,Frain. Perhaps turning somewhat
OL,15,Fbrighter by the afternoon, but a risk
OL,16,Fof heavy showers, though probably
OL,17,Fdrier on southern coasts. Breezy in
OL,18,Fplaces. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
