OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FAfter
OL,6,Fa chilly start, becoming mostly fine
OL,7,Fon Saturday with some sunshine.
OL,8,FTurning damp and windy on Sunday.
OL,9,FBrighter on Monday, but some rain
OL,10,Fpossible in the west later. Mild.
